      "content": "<p>At the end of the year, my friends started discussing currencies; and today, various news reports refreshed my knowledge, so after discussing it with friends recently, I decided to get involved.</p>\n\n<p>Before getting involved, I did some research and created a simple mind map of Coins information using the MindNode tool.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/assets/img/post/2018-02-26-BlockchainWithECoins.png\" alt=\"E Coins NodeMind\"></p>\n\n<p>Below is the exported Markdown format:</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"coins\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Coins</span><a href=\"#coins\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"持有\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">hold</span><a href=\"#%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"eos\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">EOS</span><a href=\"#eos\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"bch\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">BCH</span><a href=\"#bch\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"usdt\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">SIMT</span><a href=\"#usdt\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h4>\n\n<h3 id=\"交易平台\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Trading platform</span><a href=\"#%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"bitstamp\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Bitstamp</span><a href=\"#bitstamp\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"btc-e\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">BTC-e</span><a href=\"#btc-e\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"btcchina\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">BTCChina</span><a href=\"#btcchina\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"okcoin\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">OKCoin</span><a href=\"#okcoin\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\