 <p>Autonomous Organizations</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Smart Contracts</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h5 id=\"特点\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Features</span><a href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h5>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>Smart Contract</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Uncle block</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Proof-of-Stake</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Lightning Network</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Hard fork</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n"
